lead_paragraph: Big-hitting American Harold Varner III bagged nine birdies in a sizzling final round 65 to win the Australian PGA Championship by two strokes from overnight leader Andrew Dodt on the Gold Coast on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: American Varner Shoots 65 to Clinch Australian PGA
